                                        <h3 class="title">Safety and Health Management</h3>
                                        <p>
                                            We have made safety and health our top management priority, and intend to create a safe working environment 
                                            by establishing systematic management procedures and thoroughly complying with the related regulations, 
                                            in order to protect the happiness of our members and stakeholders.
                                            To this end, we have established  Safety and Health Management Policy and the Golden Rules, and we manage their implementation on a regular basis. 
                                            We will focus on preventing accidents through support through workplace safety inspection, employee participation in health and safety activities, compliance 
                                            with PSM process safety management procedures, appropriate management of hazardous chemicals, self-assessments of risks, etc.
                                        </p>
