                                        <p>Management Policy and Key Implementation Factors</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="shm_sub_con">
                                        <div>
                                            <p class="fix_str2"><span>Safety and Health Policy</span>We have set health and safety as our top priority in our core management values, <br class="br_pc">and will continuously manage it in the following six categories.</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">1</span>
                                                    <span>Core Value</span>
                                                    Setting the core values of management
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">2</span>
                                                    <span>Legal Compliance</span>
                                                    Compliance with safety regulations
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">3</span>
                                                    <span>System Process</span>
                                                    Safety and health system management
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">4</span>
                                                    <span>Leadership</span>
                                                    Executives and managers leading by setting examples
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">5</span>
                                                    <span>Competency</span>
                                                    Cultivation of risk prediction capabilities
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">6</span>
                                                    <span>Culture</span>
                                                    Establishment of a safety culture
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <div>
                                                <img src="/resources/service/env/images/sustain/shm_rule01_en.png" alt="shm_rule01">
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="shm_sub_con_line"></div>
                                        <div>
                                            <p><span>Safety<br> Golden Rule</span>We have established seven Golden Rules for the eradication of serious accidents (falls, suffocation, etc.), <br class="br_pc">and all our members, including our employees and contractors, must practice them as a basic principle.</p>
                                            <div>
