                                            </div>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">1</span>
                                                    <span>Self-assessment of risks</span>
                                                    <p>Conducting annual self-assessments of risks, according to the circumstances of each business site, <br class="br_pc">and improving the level of safety management through regular risk assessments and certification</p>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">2</span>
                                                    <span>Inspections and support</span>
                                                    <p>Inspection of workplace safety management by the head office and <br class="br_pc">regional safety management organizations</p>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <span class="shm_sub_con_num">3</span>
